Page[73]=new Array("The Oracle Directory Server is required only if you are using Reporting.","To prepare the Oracle Directory Server:","Install the Oracle Directory Server.","For more information, see Step 1: Install the Oracle Directory Server.","Create the ORACLEHS namespace and crnsysadmin user on the Oracle Directory Server.","For more information, see Step 2: Create the ORACLEHS organizational unit (OU) and crnsysadmin user on the Oracle Directory Server.","Note: You must also create an ORACLEHS namespace and a crnsysadmin user on the Cognos Content Manager Server. For more information, see Create the ORACLEHS LDAP namespace.","Steps to prepare the Oracle Directory Server","178924.htm");
